{"tid":1237791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣：重申當日示威者無人是暴徒","createTime":"2019-06-17T15:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T09:22:13.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1445,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":116,"replies":[{"pid":"4ca9a8d31a5efb4ebc35d30bb3dd806ced09af3b","tid":1237791,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:39:26.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】立法會議員區諾軒批評警方只控告五人暴動罪，目的為分化示威者，又稱不可接受警方仍以暴動形容示威者的行為。<br />\n<br />\n而民陣則重申當日的示威者沒有一人為暴徒，認為警務處處長盧偉聰的說法，未有撤回將當日示威視為暴動的定性，沒有回應市民的訴求，要求他問責下台。"},{"pid":"b54d09a07e293ef88b15ab5e4924e0badeb901ea","tid":1237791,"uid":20933,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:39:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=352111\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D352111&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYaix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=f0066743\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D352111&h=e8df6a25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=352111</a>"},{"pid":"d8fdef76dd11c511d870e09f608eeb969442955d","tid":1237791,"uid":54303,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c75269c77fd8296498b4703045dee4a1b343dc","tid":1237791,"uid":28870,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:41:23.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"1f195afcf164a32c2e96692b547e78a31aeef50e","tid":1237791,"uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:41:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b19286d931dc7dabe3e2656479c596684e77aa9","tid":1237791,"uid":37528,"like":87,"dislike":0,"score":87,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:41:31.000Z","msg":"一齊合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\"